1
00:00:07,340 --> 00:00:10,260
=Dungeon Archive=

2
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:11,680
The killer is...

3
00:00:12,760 --> 00:00:13,800
Ding Pillar.

4
00:00:16,220 --> 00:00:18,220
(The killer)

5
00:00:18,460 --> 00:00:19,860
(The killer is caught)

6
00:00:19,860 --> 00:00:21,220
(Ding Pillar)

7
00:00:21,220 --> 00:00:23,200
(Case reconstruction)

8
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:24,560
I'm the killer,

9
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:26,040
Ding Pillar.

10
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:27,000
Once I realized

11
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,720
I might actually be undead,

12
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:31,960
I went straight after Ke Stubborn.

13
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:33,960
Then I remembered Lord Tui saying

14
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:37,640
that Qianji Pavilion had intel
on the kingdoms of Tui, Li, and Kuang.

15
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:39,360
I had to see it for myself.

16
00:00:39,360 --> 00:00:40,680
(Qianji Pavilion)
So I headed to Qianji Pavilion.

17
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:43,120
This was Chancellor Tui's turf.

18
00:00:43,120 --> 00:00:45,280
Inside, I found a massive war table.

19
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:47,000
(Weaken the Li Kingdom)
There was a drawer built into the side.

20
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:49,360
It was labeled "Weaken the Li Kingdom".

21
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:52,440
It laid out a plan to work
with the Li Kingdom's fake crown prince

22
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:54,800
and have the pawn take out the real one.

23
00:00:55,440 --> 00:00:57,280
The real crown prince wanted peace,

24
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:58,360
so he had to go.

25
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:01,080
The fake prince, on the other hand,
was completely useless.

26
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:02,760
That made him the perfect puppet.

27
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:04,360
He could be dealt with later.

28
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:05,400
What?

29
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,760
Ke Stubborn tried to assassinate me?

30
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:10,040
And Chancellor Tui ordered it?

31
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:11,080
What was he really plotting

32
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:14,520
(Weaken the Li Kingdom)
across all three kingdoms?

33
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:15,520
Whatever it was,

34
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:17,560
it was bad news,

35
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:18,560
which meant

36
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,360
Chancellor Tui had to die.

37
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,040
(Alchemy Room)
I also found a key to the alchemy room.

38
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:25,320
I'd just walked past it.

39
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:26,040
It was nearby.

40
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,760
(Alchemy Room)
I went straight there.

41
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:30,480
Other than a huge furnace,

42
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:32,680
there was nowhere to hide.

43
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:35,320
After looking around

44
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,840
and going through his decree,

45
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:39,920
I realized the furnace
was big enough to hide in.

46
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:42,280
Chancellor Tui always brewed alone.

47
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:44,960
Three minutes in, he would open the lid.

48
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,840
That's when the plan came to me.

49
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,520
By then, I knew

50
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:50,040
I'd come back from the dead.

51
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:53,920
Once the servants added the herbs,

52
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,800
I could slip inside
while they went to get water.

53
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,600
Then I'd bury myself under the herbs.

54
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:01,080
The servants would come back
and fill it with water.

55
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:03,480
I could stay underwater
without breathing.

56
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,200
After the Nether Elders
checked everything,

57
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,480
they sealed the lid.

58
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,000
I waited underwater

59
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,720
for Chancellor Tui to open the lid.

60
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:14,520
Then the lid finally opened.

61
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,440
I reached out,

62
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:18,480
grabbed him,
and pulled his head underwater.

63
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,400
I was far stronger than him.

64
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,800
He never stood a chance.

65
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,160
Within moments, he went still.

66
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:24,920
I dumped him on the floor

67
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,800
and climbed out.

68
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:29,200
Once I was sure he was dead,

69
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:30,720
I climbed back inside.

70
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:33,920
Eventually,
the people outside would notice,

71
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:34,800
come in to check,

72
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,640
and find his body.

73
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:38,240
Once they carried him out,

74
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,640
I could slip away.

75
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,800
But the second I got back inside,

76
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:44,520
his body started moving.

77
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,320
Then he started coughing up water.

78
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,360
What the hell?

79
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,800
How was he still alive?

80
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:52,840
I'd checked. He was dead.

81
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:55,200
The firewood was soaked
and couldn't be relit,

82
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:57,480
and he was soaked from head to toe.

83
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:58,840
Once he came to,

84
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,760
he tore off his soaked robe

85
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:02,840
and stormed out.

86
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,640
A few minutes passed.

87
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:06,440
Once it was quiet,

88
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:08,520
I crawled out.

89
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,360
Still trying to make sense of it, I left

90
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:12,720
and pretended nothing happened.

91
00:03:13,740 --> 00:03:15,980
(TNT, Ding Chengxin player log archive)

92
00:03:16,020 --> 00:03:17,220
(Identity: Ding Pillar,
Crown Prince of Li Kingdom)

93
00:03:17,220 --> 00:03:17,980
(End the wars, reclaim the seal,
and restore the realm)

94
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,080
I'm Ding Chengxin.

95
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:23,640
I play Ding Pillar,
the Crown Prince of the Li Kingdom,

96
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:25,120
and the killer in this case.

97
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:27,640
We all accepted
Chancellor Tui's invitation

98
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,920
to the Zuixian Inn.

99
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:30,960
Not long after we ate,

100
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,440
he coughed up blood and collapsed.

101
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:36,840
Then the room went dark,
and he dropped from the ceiling,

102
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,080
dead right in front of us.

103
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:42,160
(Hiding my relief)
That was when I knew he was really dead.

104
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,800
Unlike when I drowned him
two days earlier,

105
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,760
this time, he wasn't coming back.

106
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,280
As we investigated,

107
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,880
I realized none of us
originally wanted Chancellor Tui dead.

108
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:54,800
(Everyone had a target)

109
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,640
We were all after one another,

110
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,840
and each of us had attacked
someone another person hated.

111
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,400
All on the same day.

112
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,920
That's why our bodies

113
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:05,120
were taken to the Chivalry Manor.

114
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,120
Pretty sure he's dead.

115
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,400
Because each of us had died once.

116
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,440
(Rebuilding the timeline
from memory)

117
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:10,320
Then everyone went to Qianji Pavilion.

118
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:13,720
I'd secretly been there
two days earlier.

119
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:16,070
I only looked at what concerned me

120
00:04:16,070 --> 00:04:17,950
and took my Crown Prince's seal.

121
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:18,920
(Removing the clue that points to him)

122
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,760
The evidence showed

123
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:21,320
that Chancellor Tui

124
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,880
was actually Chancellor Kuang.

125
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:23,680
He was after total control.

126
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,420
(Clues reveal Chancellor Tui's plan)
He wanted to rule the world.

127
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:27,840
So, he ruined all our lives to do it.

128
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:31,120
(Connecting the dots)
Now we all had a motive to kill him.

129
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:33,200
The group believed
whoever had visited Qianji Pavilion

130
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,880
and taken something

131
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,380
(Starting with the motive)
was more likely

132
00:04:36,380 --> 00:04:37,880
(Motive made them a stronger suspect)
to be the killer.

133
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,600
They also suspected the missing item

134
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,840
was my Crown Prince's seal.

135
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:44,600
What you stole from Qianji Pavilion
that day was...

136
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:47,240
Just like that, all eyes were on me.

137
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,880
(Keeping his cool under pressure)
I had to play it cool.

138
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:51,200
Luckily, they also considered
that the killer

139
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:53,720
might have stolen
Chancellor Kuang's fake seal.

140
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:54,720
Chancellor Kuang had a forged seal?

141
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,160
And whoever stole it

142
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:58,160
might have wanted to clear
the Longdong Army's name.

143
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:59,320
The seal used back then was fake.

144
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:01,320
So I quickly raised another possibility,

145
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:04,240
guiding everyone to think
about who would steal it

146
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:06,200
(Steering the discussion)
for that reason.

147
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:08,600
Just like that, the heat moved off me.

148
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,560
In the alchemy room,

149
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,360
everyone learned
that Chancellor Tui's condition

150
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,720
was tied
to the half-brewed Qide Longdong potion

151
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,800
when I attacked him.

152
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,000
His face was soaked,

153
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:20,320
and he mumbled,
"What's happening"?

154
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:21,760
That's why his death

155
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:24,160
matched the wooden plaque exactly.

156
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,560
(Rebuilding the murder
from the evidence)

157
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,640
We were still alive

158
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:30,400
because we'd all drunk
the Qide Longdong potion.

159
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:33,560
It also wipes out the memory
of your death.

160
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,240
Memory?

161
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,560
That's why Chancellor Tui and all of us

162
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,920
couldn't remember how we died.

163
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,880
(The clues explain the memory loss)

164
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,440
In the final discussion,

165
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:44,120
everyone analyzed the timeline

166
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:47,640
(Reading the room)
and who would have stolen the item.

167
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:50,040
Ning Waver, Yang Glory, and I

168
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:52,120
ended up as the top suspects.

169
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:54,680
Since I had woken up earliest
after being killed,

170
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:57,640
I supposedly had the most time
to kill him.

171
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,160
(Picking the best scapegoat)
So I voted for Yang Glory,

172
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,400
(Voting Window: Yang Glory)
pushing the vote further off track.

173
00:06:02,980 --> 00:06:05,220
(Liu Yuning player log archive)

174
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:06,260
(Identity: Ning Waver,
Longdong Army's Young Marshal)

175
00:06:06,260 --> 00:06:07,420
(His family slain,
he hides to avenge them)

176
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:09,000
I'm Liu Yuning.

177
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,360
I play the senior disciple
of Shi Damen Sect,

178
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,640
Ning Waver.

179
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,400
But that's not my real identity.

180
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,800
I'm the young marshal
of the Longdong Army,

181
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:17,840
Young General Dong.

182
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,280
(Zuixian Inn)
Before noon,

183
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:22,280
we all arrived outside the inn

184
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:24,920
for Chancellor Tui's banquet.

185
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,400
Then I saw

186
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,680
Yang Glory, the woman I'd killed
the day before.

187
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,320
(Watching and waiting)
She was alive.

188
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:32,200
Before I could process it,

189
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:34,200
Chancellor Tui dropped dead.

190
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:37,000
As we investigated,

191
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,680
(Suspicious clues about Ning Waver)
everyone knew who I really was.

192
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,040
My true identity

193
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:42,200
was the son
of the Longdong Army's commander,

194
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:43,600
Young General Dong.

195
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,400
They also discovered

196
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:46,000
that I believed Yang Glory

197
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:48,600
was a spy from the Li Kingdom
who had destroyed the Longdong Army.

198
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,960
(Revealing his target to clear himself)
Yang Glory!

199
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:51,240
She was the one I wanted dead.

200
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,040
But then came the real shock.

201
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:54,000
Your buddy cooks.

202
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,920
While searching Yang Glory's woodshed,

203
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,800
I realized I had her all wrong.

204
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,200
She was my closest friend

205
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,220
(Clues clear things up)
in the army,

206
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,120
Dian.

207
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:05,320
She had been disguised as a boy,

208
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,880
and I'd later changed my appearance,

209
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:09,160
so neither of us recognized the other.

210
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,480
I couldn't accept it.

211
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,360
I didn't want it to be true.

212
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,200
She was your Dian.

213
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:17,880
Because I'd already attacked Yang Glory.

214
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,840
Later at the Chivalry Manor,
we found out

215
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:23,800
that Yang, He, Ke, Ding, and I

216
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,040
had all died.

217
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,640
I'm the only living person here.
Don't drag me into this.

218
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:29,160
We all had motives against one another

219
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,040
and had each carried out a murder plan,

220
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:35,800
(The motives don't match the victim)
but no one wanted Chancellor Tui dead.

221
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,720
Then,

222
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:39,080
(Qianji Pavilion held kingdom intel)
we found dirt on Chancellor Tui.

223
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:41,280
Secret intel on the kingdoms
of Tui, Li, and Kuang.

224
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:44,000
The clue led us to Qianji Pavilion.

225
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,320
It really is Qianji Pavilion.

226
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:47,360
There, we also discovered
that the killer

227
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,120
(A drawer in the war table was opened)
had opened a drawer

228
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:50,560
and taken a key clue.

229
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,060
A key item was missing.

230
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,200
So we worked backward.

231
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:55,000
If each suspect were the killer,

232
00:07:55,020 --> 00:07:55,820
(Tracking the missing clue)
then what secret

233
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:57,160
(Working backward from motive)
would they have seen,

234
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,200
and what evidence would they have taken?

235
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,160
Then I had a crazy thought.

236
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:00,600
I have a thought,

237
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,240
but I could be wrong.

238
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,480
Could the missing item
be the Li Kingdom's Crown Prince's seal?

239
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:05,920
(Connecting the clues)
What if Ding Pillar saw

240
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,960
(A bold theory)
that his own seal was here?

241
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:10,160
With it, he could prove who he was

242
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,640
and take back his life.

243
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,280
That theory

244
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:15,960
put Ding at the top of my list.

245
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,200
Then, in the alchemy room...

246
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:19,720
Enter the alchemy room...

247
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:22,960
I realized the brewing process
gave the killer a perfect opening.

248
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,240
After the furnace was filled with water,

249
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,600
(Connecting the known clues)
someone could hide inside.

250
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,720
(Rebuilding the killer's route)

251
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,480
When the lid was opened to add herbs,

252
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,880
whoever was inside

253
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:32,380
could kill him.

254
00:08:32,380 --> 00:08:33,520
(Refining the murder plan)

255
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,400
And all of us

256
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:38,440
had unknowingly drunk
the Qide Longdong potion earlier.

257
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,550
We had all died once.

258
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,960
(Resurrection made hiding possible)
We didn't need to breathe.

259
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,400
so we could hide
inside the water-filled furnace.

260
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:44,880
In the end,

261
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:47,680
we used the flower buds
to build a rough timeline.

262
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,140
(Linking timeline and motive)
Once we considered

263
00:08:49,140 --> 00:08:50,360
(Confirming the killer)
who took the missing item,

264
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:53,560
I voted for the prime suspect,

265
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,160
Ding Pillar.

266
00:08:55,180 --> 00:08:57,460
(Zhang Linghe player log archive)

267
00:08:57,540 --> 00:08:58,540
(Identity: He Ha,
Crown Prince of Tui Kingdom)

268
00:08:58,540 --> 00:08:59,740
(Lay down arms, protect the innocent)

269
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,000
I'm Zhang Linghe.

270
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,720
I play
the wandering fortune-teller He Ha

271
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,840
while secretly hiding my real identity

272
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,720
as Prince Tui,

273
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,160
the Crown Prince of the Tui Kingdom.

274
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,560
I was framed by a traitor

275
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,360
and stripped of my status for treason.

276
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,200
That's how I ended up living
as a wanderer.

277
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,200
He Ha.

278
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:15,640
For years, I've been searching
for the man who ruined me,

279
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,800
the Crown Prince of the Li Kingdom.

280
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:18,640
I never expected
to find him in Tui City,

281
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,160
hiding under the name Ding Pillar.

282
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:22,960
(An old grudge remains)
My enemy was right before me.

283
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,600
I had to settle the score.

284
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:27,360
So on 30 May, I slipped into his room

285
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,600
and killed him.

286
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:31,040
But things took a bizarre turn.

287
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,240
(Zuixian Inn)
At noon today,

288
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:35,000
I went to meet Chancellor Tui
at the inn,

289
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:38,400
where Ding Pillar was present.
He was alive and unharmed.

290
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:39,640
(The dead came back. Something's off)
How was that possible?

291
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,360
After killing him,
I'd checked his breathing

292
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:43,440
and confirmed he was dead.

293
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,520
None of it made sense.

294
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,120
Before I could investigate further,

295
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:50,440
Chancellor Tui suddenly died
at the banquet.

296
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:52,400
Who killed him?

297
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,520
As we investigated,

298
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:55,840
a few things didn't add up.

299
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:58,400
First, each of us wanted
to kill someone else,

300
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:00,720
(Checking the motives)
but no one wanted Chancellor Tui dead.

301
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,520
(No motive to kill)
No one.

302
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:04,200
Second, we had all killed one another,

303
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,840
yet every victim had come back to life.

304
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:09,720
So who wanted Chancellor Tui dead?

305
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:12,560
And how had we all come back?

306
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:14,680
At the Chivalry Manor, we found a clue

307
00:10:14,680 --> 00:10:16,000
that answered part of the mystery.

308
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:16,760
A little leverage?

309
00:10:16,760 --> 00:10:17,640
The evidence showed

310
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:19,200
that Chancellor Tui had a secret

311
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:22,040
involving the kingdoms
of Tui, Li, and Kuang.

312
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:23,680
Besides, every suspect's past

313
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:25,120
was tied to those three kingdoms.

314
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,080
(Uncovering hidden motives)

315
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,880
All of them had also been taken
to the Chivalry Manor.

316
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:29,160
(Body Collection Record)
Four bodies collected.

317
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:31,520
(Connecting everyone's stories)
Which meant the killer likely woke up

318
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,500
(Rebuilding their movements)
at the Chivalry Manor,

319
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,840
learned Chancellor Tui's secret,

320
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,200
and decided to kill him.

321
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,520
The evidence at Qianji Pavilion

322
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:39,760
backed up my theory.

323
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:43,720
To conquer the kingdoms
of Tui, Li, and Kuang,

324
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:45,760
Chancellor Tui had framed several of us

325
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:47,200
or threatened people we cared about.

326
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:49,160
So after each of us

327
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:50,640
saw the secrets in Qianji Pavilion,

328
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:53,240
(The evidence gives everyone a motive)
we all had a reason to kill him.

329
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:55,680
We also found proof

330
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:58,760
that one of us
had visited Qianji Pavilion

331
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,880
and taken a key item from a drawer.

332
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:02,560
Something had been taken.

333
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:03,200
Then,

334
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,380
we solved the mystery
of our resurrection.

335
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:09,120
We had all drunk
the Qide Longdong potion.

336
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:11,760
Anyone who took it
would revive after death

337
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:13,640
(Potion made the murder possible)
with superhuman strength.

338
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,840
Their wounds would heal rapidly.

339
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:15,680
The killer

340
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:18,160
used that enhanced body after dying

341
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,320
to kill Chancellor Tui.

342
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,000
To take him out.

343
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:20,680
At the same time,

344
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:23,200
Chancellor Tui's notes
on improving the potion

345
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:25,880
(Matching the brew to his breakdown)
revealed when he had actually died.

346
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,480
(Determining the true time of death)
The drug took effect two days earlier.

347
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,760
In fact, Chancellor Tui

348
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:31,680
had drunk the undercooked potion
two days ago

349
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,720
and had been killed by the murderer.

350
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:36,360
He didn't go berserk
and die until today,

351
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:39,480
which explains the condition
of his face.

352
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,040
During the final deduction,

353
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:43,400
we determined the killer
had to meet several conditions.

354
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:45,480
First, the killer had to have died once.

355
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,600
He had already taken the potion?

356
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:48,640
Only someone with that enhanced body

357
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:49,920
could carry out the murder.

358
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:51,800
(Using breath and timing)
No one alive could last three minutes.

359
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:52,560
(to narrow the suspect)

360
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:53,200
Second,

361
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:55,760
the killer needed plenty of time to act.

362
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:57,480
That ruled me out.

363
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:00,160
Third, besides Chancellor Tui,

364
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:01,760
we all had an original enemy
we wanted dead.

365
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:03,920
After killing Chancellor Kuang,
the killer still chose to kill

366
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:05,360
the person they had hated before.

367
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:05,880
Why?

368
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:08,080
Because in the killer's mind,

369
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:10,360
(Analyzing the killer's mindset)
that person sided with Chancellor Kuang.

370
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,280
(Narrowing the suspect pool further)

371
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:12,960
And judging by the outcome,

372
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:15,240
everyone attacked their original target.

373
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:18,880
So the real killer
had to meet one more condition.

374
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:20,080
Both of these people tried to kill me.

375
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,840
Even knowing Chancellor Tui's secret,

376
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,920
(Using a second attack)
they still went after their target.

377
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:24,640
(to narrow the suspect)

378
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:26,440
I believed Yang Glory and Ding Pillar,

379
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:28,240
after seeing Qianji Pavilion's secrets,
had motives

380
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:30,880
(Screening suspects from the deduction)
to kill Ke and Chancellor Tui.

381
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,320
That fits a route where they woke
at the Chivalry Manor

382
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,560
and killed two people.

383
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,520
Of the two, Yang Glory

384
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:38,520
had more time to kill him.

385
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:41,240
So, I voted for Yang Glory.

386
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,740
(Yang Glory)

387
00:12:42,780 --> 00:12:45,060
(Zhou Keyu player log archive)

388
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:46,060
(Identity: Ke Stubborn,
Princess Kuang's secret guard)

389
00:12:46,060 --> 00:12:47,340
(A fallen homeland, a lone guard)

390
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:49,080
I'm Zhou Keyu.

391
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:52,760
I play the young martial arts prodigy,
Ke Stubborn,

392
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:55,160
and Princess Kuang's chief secret guard.

393
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,240
While solving the previous case,

394
00:12:57,240 --> 00:13:01,520
I discovered that He Ha was a member
of the Tui Kingdom's royal family.

395
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:02,800
To prevent future trouble,

396
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:04,760
I went to investigate his room.

397
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:07,360
I confirmed he was indeed Tui royalty,

398
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:09,760
so I strangled him with a belt.

399
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,760
But somehow, he appeared

400
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:14,160
right in front of me again.

401
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,320
How was that possible?

402
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,480
(Completely baffled)

403
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:19,440
After arriving at Zuixian Inn
as invited,

404
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:21,520
I noticed Chancellor Tui spoke

405
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:23,400
exactly like Chancellor Kuang
from my homeland.

406
00:13:23,420 --> 00:13:24,640
(Spotting something suspicious)

407
00:13:24,640 --> 00:13:27,280
Could Chancellor Tui
actually be Chancellor Kuang?

408
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:29,180
(Recognizing a familiar voice)
Was he now

409
00:13:29,180 --> 00:13:30,600
(Questioning his identity)
a powerful figure in the Tui Kingdom?

410
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,720
As we investigated,

411
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,160
the princess told me

412
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:35,080
she had no intention
of restoring the Kuang Kingdom.

413
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:37,160
Then were all the orders
Chancellor Kuang gave me

414
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,800
completely fabricated?

415
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:41,200
What did that make everything I'd done?

416
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,320
(Inferring the chancellor forged
the orders)

417
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:44,080
The clues showed me

418
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:46,640
that all of us had motives
against one another,

419
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:49,520
but none of us had any motive
against Chancellor Tui.

420
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:52,960
At the Chivalry Manor,
we discovered that everyone except Jin

421
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:55,360
had died and come back to life.

422
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,880
That had to be the key to the case.

423
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,240
At Qianji Pavilion,

424
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,800
we learned Chancellor Tui's

425
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:03,160
real goal was to conquer
all three kingdoms

426
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:04,640
and rule the world himself.

427
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:06,640
But someone had visited
and taken something

428
00:14:06,640 --> 00:14:08,800
(Key evidence missing)
from a hidden compartment.

429
00:14:08,800 --> 00:14:10,580
(Using the missing item as a clue)
So who would need something

430
00:14:10,580 --> 00:14:12,480
(to find out the killer's motive)
from Qianji Pavilion?

431
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:14,280
Our investigation showed

432
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:16,720
that everyone had a reason to go there.

433
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:19,960
Ning, He, and Yang needed evidence

434
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,880
proving the Longdong Army
wasn't made up of traitors.

435
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:26,440
Ding needed the seal
that proved his identity.

436
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:29,800
And everyone guessed I might want

437
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:31,520
evidence that could restore
the Kuang Kingdom.

438
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:33,680
In the alchemy room,

439
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:35,000
we finally discovered

440
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:37,440
(Solving the resurrection mystery)
why Chancellor Tui came back to life.

441
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,760
Just like him,

442
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:40,280
we had all drunk
the Qide Longdong potion.

443
00:14:40,280 --> 00:14:43,040
But Chancellor Tui
had drunk it undercooked.

444
00:14:44,160 --> 00:14:45,920
This murder method required

445
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,840
the killer to hide
inside the alchemy furnace.

446
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:50,400
So the killer had to be someone
who had already died.

447
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:52,120
(Analyzing the conditions required
to hide in the furnace)

448
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:54,160
The killer had to meet two conditions.

449
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:54,720
First,

450
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,800
they had to know before 30 May
that Chancellor Tui

451
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:58,880
(Checking the requirements)
would brew medicine at 11PM.

452
00:14:58,880 --> 00:14:59,640
(Key info required to kill him)

453
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:02,000
Second,
they had to visit Qianji Pavilion.

454
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:04,400
At first,
I suspected Ning Waver the most.

455
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:05,520
He had died first,

456
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,360
(Checking the conditions)
so he had the most time to act.

457
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,680
(Ning Waver had plenty of time)
It had to be Ning.

458
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:09,960
But Ning made a strong point.

459
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,600
After killing Chancellor Tui,

460
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:13,360
he had no reason to kill Yang as well.

461
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:17,640
That left someone with motives
against Chancellor Tui

462
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:18,960
and their original target.

463
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,920
(Analyzing the killer's mindset)
They needed motives against both.

464
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:22,300
(Narrowing the suspects)
The only people

465
00:15:22,300 --> 00:15:23,600
who met every condition
were Ding and Yang.

466
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,920
In my view,

467
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:28,440
Ding had a much more urgent reason
to retrieve his Crown Prince's seal.

468
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:31,640
So I voted for Ding Pillar.

469
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:33,300
(Voting Window: Ding Pillar)

470
00:15:33,340 --> 00:15:35,580
(Yang Chaoyue player log archive)

471
00:15:35,620 --> 00:15:36,580
(Identity: Yang Glory,
Thousand-Faced Eagle King's founder)

472
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:37,860
(A thousand faces, one righteous cause)

473
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:39,800
I'm Yang Chaoyue.

474
00:15:39,800 --> 00:15:42,000
I play the cook at Truth Inn,

475
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,320
Yang Glory.

476
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,160
I also

477
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:46,080
have a hidden identity,

478
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:47,560
founder
of the Thousand-Faced Eagle King.

479
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:48,360
(A thousand faces, one righteous cause)

480
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:49,800
On the morning of 1 June,

481
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:53,120
we went to Zuixian Inn
at Chancellor Tui's banquet.

482
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:55,360
There, I saw someone
who had already been killed,

483
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:56,880
Ke Stubborn.

484
00:15:57,920 --> 00:15:59,540
(Growing suspicious)
He was alive.

485
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:01,800
And he acted as nothing had happened.

486
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:02,960
How was that possible?

487
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:06,720
After we sampled the tea
and snacks Chancellor Tui prepared,

488
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:09,080
he suddenly jumped onto the table

489
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:09,760
and died.

490
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:13,480
As we investigated,

491
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:15,200
I discovered my true identity.

492
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:17,680
(Clues reveal her past)
I was born in the Li Kingdom.

493
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:19,080
(Birth Record: Li Kingdom)
My birth name was Li Shishui.

494
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:21,160
But because of the war,

495
00:16:21,160 --> 00:16:23,840
I was abandoned
on the streets of Tui City.

496
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:26,000
My adoptive father,
a Longdong Army soldier, took me in,

497
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,800
and I later joined the army with him.

498
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:29,000
It turned out Ning Waver

499
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,200
was the boy I'd known as a child,

500
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,640
my closest friend

501
00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:32,320
in the Longdong Army.

502
00:16:32,340 --> 00:16:33,560
(The keepsakes match perfectly)

503
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:34,960
But because of a misunderstanding,

504
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:36,200
he now wanted to kill me.

505
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:38,280
At the same time,

506
00:16:38,280 --> 00:16:40,240
we uncovered everyone's motives.

507
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,760
They were all directed at one another,

508
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:43,440
(Sorting through everyone's motives)
not at Chancellor Tui.

509
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,680
(No motive against the victim found yet)
No one wanted him dead.

510
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:46,480
Even more shocking,

511
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:47,840
every one of us had acted

512
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:49,200
and killed our own enemy.

513
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:52,200
Yet every victim mysteriously came back
from the dead.

514
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,520
Don't know why he's still alive.

515
00:16:53,520 --> 00:16:56,280
I believed that while I was asleep
the night before,

516
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,820
(Combining everyone's testimony)
someone had killed me.

517
00:16:57,820 --> 00:16:58,480
(Guessing deep sleep was murder)

518
00:16:58,480 --> 00:17:00,320
That would explain
why I woke up somewhere else.

519
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:03,900
(Blood confirmed it)
I came back to bloodstained bedding.

520
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:06,720
We rescued Junzi Ruyu and Yan Reason

521
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:08,880
and obtained an important clue
about Chancellor Tui.

522
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:10,280
Secret intel on the kingdoms
of Tui, Li, and Kuang.

523
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:12,070
He was actually Chancellor Kuang,

524
00:17:12,070 --> 00:17:13,800
hiding in the Tui Kingdom
and stirring up conflict.

525
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:17,440
He used the Qide Longdong potion
to create superhuman undead soldiers

526
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,240
(Clues explain the resurrection)

527
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:19,560
and planned to conquer the world.

528
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:22,240
Thankfully,
that monster had already been killed.

529
00:17:22,830 --> 00:17:24,440
But who killed him?

530
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,200
(Tracing the clues to the killer)

531
00:17:25,200 --> 00:17:27,960
Ding needed his Crown Prince's seal
to confront his younger brother.

532
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:30,120
With the seal, you could go back
and confront your brother.

533
00:17:30,120 --> 00:17:32,400
Ding's brother
was Chancellor Kuang's puppet,

534
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:33,960
so the two were very familiar.

535
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:36,400
Ding may have disguised himself
as his brother

536
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:37,600
(Using Ding Pillar's identity)
to get close to Chancellor Kuang.

537
00:17:37,600 --> 00:17:38,280
(to hypothesize the murder method)

538
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:39,720
In the final round,

539
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:42,160
suspicion centered on Ding and me.

540
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:45,240
Everyone thought we had more time

541
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,680
to kill Chancellor Tui.

542
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:48,400
I knew I wasn't the killer.

543
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:50,840
A lot of our timelines overlapped,

544
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:51,840
but the most suspicious person...

545
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:53,600
So I voted Ding Pillar.

546
00:17:53,600 --> 00:17:54,780
(Voting Window: Ding Pillar)

547
00:17:54,820 --> 00:17:57,100
(Jin Jing player log archive)

548
00:17:57,140 --> 00:17:58,020
(Identity: Jin Thrifty,
Princess of Kuang Kingdom)

549
00:17:58,020 --> 00:17:58,860
(Leave war behind, live in peace)

550
00:17:59,120 --> 00:18:00,520
I'm Jin Jing.

551
00:18:00,520 --> 00:18:04,520
I play Jin Thrifty,
the Princess of the Kuang Kingdom.

552
00:18:04,520 --> 00:18:07,120
A few days had passed
since the last case.

553
00:18:07,120 --> 00:18:10,920
Days earlier, Chancellor Tui invited us
to a banquet.

554
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:14,520
We agreed to meet today at Zuixian Inn.

555
00:18:14,520 --> 00:18:15,960
We showed up dressed for the banquet,

556
00:18:15,960 --> 00:18:19,840
and Chancellor Tui welcomed us in.

557
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:21,880
We had barely started talking

558
00:18:22,520 --> 00:18:23,920
when he suddenly died.

559
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:26,560
Since I had no chance to kill him,

560
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:29,400
I was the only one cleared
to investigate.

561
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,720
I started with the crime scene.

562
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:34,040
(Brothers in every life)
I found clues about the Longdong Army.

563
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:34,720
(A bond beyond death
Shi Damen's gift to General Dong)

564
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:35,980
(Using evidence found at the scene)
That revealed

565
00:18:35,980 --> 00:18:37,440
(Uncovering the suspect's past)
Ning Waver's real identity.

566
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:39,080
I'm Young General Dong.

567
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:41,520
He insisted he had nothing to do
with Chancellor Tui's death.

568
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,450
The person he wanted to kill
was Yang Glory.

569
00:18:44,450 --> 00:18:45,600
(Mapping everyone's targets)
Yang Glory!

570
00:18:45,600 --> 00:18:49,200
Yang Glory said she wanted
to kill Ke Stubborn.

571
00:18:49,760 --> 00:18:51,880
Ke Stubborn wanted to kill

572
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:54,440
He Ha, the Crown Prince
of the Tui Kingdom.

573
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:56,240
He Ha hated

574
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:58,040
Ding Pillar, the Crown Prince
of the Li Kingdom.

575
00:18:58,040 --> 00:18:59,080
You wanted
Li Kingdom's crown prince dead.

576
00:18:59,080 --> 00:19:01,680
And Ding Pillar wanted
to kill Ke Stubborn.

577
00:19:02,840 --> 00:19:05,880
Their revenge motives formed
a perfect circle.

578
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:06,880
(Revealing a cycle of revenge)

579
00:19:06,880 --> 00:19:08,600
After hearing everyone's stories,

580
00:19:08,600 --> 00:19:11,200
I realized Chancellor Tui
had been stirring up trouble

581
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:12,400
across all three kingdoms.

582
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:13,480
(Uncovering the victim's agenda)
It was Chancellor Tui.

583
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:15,480
Then we went to the meeting hall.

584
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:17,080
What we found next was shocking.

585
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:19,360
(Body Collection Record)
All five of them had died.

586
00:19:20,760 --> 00:19:23,280
They also admitted
they had each killed someone.

587
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:27,320
Every victim had come back
from the dead.

588
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:30,200
On their way to kill him,

589
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:31,320
they had all seen flower buds,

590
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:34,740
(Comparing their accounts)
but each saw different buds.

591
00:19:34,740 --> 00:19:35,680
(Linking them to the timeline)

592
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:37,760
Together, we rescued Yan Reason

593
00:19:37,760 --> 00:19:39,600
and Junzi Ruyu.

594
00:19:39,600 --> 00:19:41,760
We obtained Chancellor Tui's secret

595
00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:44,600
and a letter belonging to Yan Reason.

596
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:46,440
As the pieces came together,

597
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:47,640
(Linking it to Chancellor Tui)
the case finally made sense.

598
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:49,840
(Evidence matches his symptoms)
It matches Chancellor Tui's symptoms.

599
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:51,800
We searched Qianji Pavilion

600
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:53,520
and learned that Chancellor Tui's

601
00:19:53,520 --> 00:19:56,120
real goal was to conquer
all three kingdoms

602
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:56,920
and put himself on the throne.

603
00:19:56,920 --> 00:19:58,360
He wanted to be the king.

604
00:19:58,360 --> 00:20:00,680
Nothing was ever enough for him.

605
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:03,000
That morning's tea banquet

606
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:04,440
was a trap from the start.

607
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:08,280
Then one crucial clue came back to me.

608
00:20:08,280 --> 00:20:10,920
A craftsman's letter
to Chancellor Kuang mentioned

609
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:12,200
(A drawer in the war table was opened)

610
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:15,200
(The contents had been disturbed)
that war-table drawer had been searched.

611
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:16,440
(Using the missing-item clue)
So, I believed the stolen item

612
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:19,200
(to trace the motive)
was the Li's true Crown Prince's seal.

613
00:20:19,200 --> 00:20:20,240
With the seal,

614
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,520
you could go back
and confront your brother.

615
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:25,080
I believed Ding Pillar
had been there before us.

616
00:20:25,720 --> 00:20:26,880
He took the real seal

617
00:20:26,880 --> 00:20:29,160
to expose his impostor brother.

618
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:29,840
The real seal!

619
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:34,600
A wanted notice for the flower keeper
finally made the timeline click.

620
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:35,920
(Using the flowers as a clock)
I knew how

621
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:39,360
(Rebuilding everyone's timeline)
to build the timeline from the buds.

622
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:42,160
At 6PM, there were three open flowers.

623
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:44,760
By 7PM, they had closed.

624
00:20:44,760 --> 00:20:48,240
That placed He's attempt to kill Ding
at 6PM.

625
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,840
The flower thief stole the flowers

626
00:20:49,840 --> 00:20:52,320
at around 11PM on 30 May.

627
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:53,200
At 11PM...

628
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:55,280
We determined Yang killed Ke

629
00:20:55,280 --> 00:20:56,720
after 12AM.

630
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:58,000
(The missing flowers set the timeline)
After 12AM.

631
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,600
Combining that with the timeline,

632
00:20:59,600 --> 00:21:01,160
I ruled out Ke.

633
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:02,960
He didn't have enough time,

634
00:21:02,960 --> 00:21:04,080
and his motive was weaker.

635
00:21:04,080 --> 00:21:06,400
(Eliminating suspects)
So, I mostly ruled out He as well.

636
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:08,400
After hearing everyone out,

637
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:10,320
it came down to Yang Glory

638
00:21:10,320 --> 00:21:12,480
(Narrowing it down to the killer)
and Ding Pillar.

639
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:13,640
Of the two, I chose Ding Pillar.

